	graphical_culture = africangfx
	tsonga_culture = {
		dynasty_names = {
			Mwenemutapa Rozwi Mutopa
		}
		male_names = {
			Mbire Matope Mavura Mukombero Changamire Kakuyo Neshangwe Chivere Chirisamhuru Gatsi Nyambo Siti

	salish = {			#Includes Lushootseed, Twana, and Straits Salish for now. Halkomelem and the rest of the coastal minors like Squamish, Sechelt, Nooksack, Pentlach, pre-Wakashan Comox moved to Halkomelem culture.
		primary = SAL
		dynasty_names = {
			Samish Sawehamish Semiahmoo Shishalh Siletz Skagits Skokomish Snohomish Snoqualmie Songhees Squamish Squaxin
			Stillaguamish Stolo Aitchelitz Chawathil Cheam

			Klemshkanam Tshuahntl Kwusskanam Helmits Skwaikwi Sehlekqu Shchehoos Whailanhu Sheahdelthu Kwultseh
			Kwullethu Klehkentsoot Sohnhehovs S'dehapkan Chulwhiltan Skeehtum Patchkanam Satskanam Sdzomathl Dahtldemin
			Sdzekdunum Nowachais Mislotche Sloonokshtan Moowhahladhu Toolehplan Hasehdooan Hooviltmehtum Weaipah

			Ueman Yaotl Yayauhqui Yolotli Yolyamanitzin Xicohtencatl Xiuhpilli Xihuitl Xipil Xipilli Xochitl
			Xochipepe Xochipilli Yaotl Zipactonal Zolin
		}
		female_names = {
			Quiauhxochitl Sacnite Techichpotzin Tezozomoc Tziquetzalpoztectzin
			Tezcatlan Tlacotl Tlahco Tlahcoehua Toltecatl Tonalnan Tlazozomizqui
			Yoltzin Xilonen Xiloxoch Xiuhtomiyauhtzin Xochitl Xocoh Xocoyotl Yaretzi Zeltzin Zyanya
			Acacitlu Citali Citlamina Etapali Ichtaca Icnoyotl Ilhuitl Macuilxochitl Mahuitzic Moyolehuani Moztla
			Nenetl Nochtli Papan Teoxihuitl Teuicui Tlachinolli Tlaco Tlahutli Tlalli Tlazohtzin Tlexictli Tonatzin Xihuitl
		}
	}

mosan_culture_group = {
	graphical_culture = northamericagfx

	#Note the Mosan division, one of Sapir's, is conclusively disproven as far as I'm concerned. Nevertheless, it is a valid and feasible idea to put all these troublesome little one-culture-per-group
	#cultures into a single group and call it Mosan. Is extremely attractive from a gameplay and continuity point of view, and you can't exactly say they were completely dissimilar, sharing the same
	#Sprachbund, habits, a bio region. Conversely, how much did the Waskashans really share with the Inuit, or even Alutiq, possible very distant linguistic ties asideÔ And do we really want
	#Haida all by itself or shoved in with the Athabaskan supergroupÔ I can't imagine anyone would take issue with this, unless it is to suggest adding Salishan to this group. That said, This a world
	#class cultural variety hotspot, so I'm going with Basque-like one-culture-per-group cultures here, at least for now. Old Mosan idea repurposed into a Haida group, because internal code shenanigans =p.

	haida = {			#Language isolate. Formerly placed with Athabaskan, but this is accepted to be a mistake. Attempts have been made to place it with most other groups to limited success
		primary = HDA
		dynasty_names = {
			Kiusta Kung Yan Hiellan Skidegate "Cha'atl" Haina Kaisun Cumshewa Skedans Tanu Ninstints
			Masset Atewaas Jaahguhl Kayung "Hlk'yah GaawGa" Klinkwan Sukkwan Howkan Kasaan
		}
		male_names = {
			"Nanni Chaddi" "Na tio tish" Sitahle Oahtekah Ahzaah Kootzzah Moketaveto Ohtoahnesotowheo Harkkahome
			Munamenek Otoahnisto Mahvipah Choseta Nahtan Konzhontaco Bazheech Tillaka Chacon Dasoda-hae Cochise Juh
			Delshay Goyaale
		}
		female_names = {
			Dahteste Ilthgozay Gouyen Lozen Tohayea
		}
	}
}

		Ipek Ipekel Irge Karacik Khatun KÔtyarikka KÔlnissa KÔlyamal Lyukha LÔrkka Mala Maturkka Mutlu NaÔa

			Sdzekdunum Nowachais Mislotche Sloonokshtan Moowhahladhu Toolehplan Hasehdooan Hooviltmehtum Weaipah
			S'ahanhu Shehope Hwnlahlakq Chtsimpt Tsesumten Klthahlten Kuttakanam Chlahben Noohehoos Hwehuk Pehnus

			Nemekas Puckanese Macquettequet Shimnanaquette Pakenosega Kekenutchega Chimokemow Kekenutchegun
			Muskobenense Waubonoosa Wausaquanai Minequet Otauson Tussegua Mixabee Kitchewawashen Neebeenaquin
			Anueemaycounbeeme Onewequa Nayokeeman Peshquescum Muckcumcinau Kitcheenoting Waubeekeenew
			Sheemaugua Kauguest Kitsheematush Aneuwayba Walkcaykeejugo Autowaynabee Nawgonisee owenisham

	ashanti = {
		primary = ASH
		dynasty_names = {
			"Oyoko Abohyen" Addy Afrifa Sadami Sabah Sribor Moyoyo
			#Argen
			Ekumfi Abora Enyan Knusukum Kurentsir Gomoa Ajumako Akatakyi Edina Nifa Beretuo
			Akomfrah Akoto Amankwah Ampofo Ampadu Afrakoma Daako Dankwah Baafi Bemah Boampong Boateng
			Kokote Kumankama Gyimah Frimpong Asamoah Owusu Pinaman Poku Sikafuo Twasam Tawiah Takyi
			Kwaata Manso Yamoah Ayew Nduom Nkansa Nsonwah Nyamekye Nyantakyi Nyarko Obeng Ofosu Mpong Munuo
		}
		male_names = {
			Beriguwiemda Zolgo Zongman Nengmitoni Dimani Yanza Dariziogo Luro Tutugri Zagale
			"Boadu Akofu Berempon" "Boa Amponsem" "Ntim Gyakari" "Ose Tutu" "Opoku Fofie"
			"Opoku Ware" "Kusi Obodum" "Osei Bonsu" "Osei Kojo" "Osei Kwame" "Osei Fofie" "Osei Yaw" "Kwaku Dua"
			"Salifu Saatankugri" "Mahama Kuluguba" Nyagse Zulande Zangina "Andan Sigili" Jimli Zibirim
			Gariba Yakuba Ayekeraa Kokobo Ahaha Warembe Ampen Agyinamoa Twum "Kobla Amana" Akenten
			"Obiri Yeboa" Opoku Antwi
			#Argen
			Obrumankoma Odapagya Oson Amona Anokye "Osei Kwadwo"
			Kwasi Kojo Kwabena Kwaku Yaw Kofi Kwame Berko Manu Mensa Okwan Agyenim Kumi Afuom Nkrumah

		}
		female_names = {
			Adaeze Adanna Adannaya Akachi Akuchi Amaka Schiamaka Amara Amarachi AÔuli Chi Chiamaka Chibueze Chibuike
			Chibuzo Chichi Chidi Chidiebere Chidiebube Chidiegwu Chidimma Chijindum Chika Chike Chikelu Chikere

			#Argen
			Dwirawira Manubea Akyaama Effia
